## Rule Summary

> “A great interface is not noticed. It is felt. And it never makes the user feel dumb.”

Build Fomio’s interface not to impress, but to invite — with **zero-layer, content-first navigation**, **true AMOLED dark mode**, and a theme engine that will eventually let users make Fomio feel like **their** space without ever breaking usability.
